Levels that can be awarded for building a castle are marked with an asterisk. Maximum level can also be awarded for constructing 250 castles.

===Mixed===
It is possible to advance within ranks by researching or building castles. The highest rank and level is used. For example, if a player earns the title of Prince by building two castles, they can achieve Prince level 1 by purifying 1,830 of each purified resource and holding 1,312,000 gold. If they then build a third castle, they would become a Prince level 4.

